net.sf.appia.core
Class ChannelEventRoute

java.lang.Object
  net.sf.appia.core.ChannelEventRoute

public class ChannelEventRoute
extends java.lang.Object

The route an Event will take through the Channel.
It contains the stack with only the Sessions that accept the Event.
It is the Channel counterpart of the QoSEventRoute. In practice the ChannelEventRoute is created from the QoSEventRoute.

Version:
0.1
Author:
Alexandre Pinto
